trans-unit.source: Transforms data in a Web Parts connection from a provider that implements the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartRow"></xref> interface to a consumer expecting to receive data from a provider that implements the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartParameters"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: Overfører data i en webdeler tilkobling fra en leverandør som implementerer den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartRow"> </xref> grensesnittet til en forbruker forventer å motta data fra en leverandør som implementerer den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartParameters"> </xref> grensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: Transformers are used in a Web Parts connection to translate data between two Web Parts controls with incompatible connection points.
trans-unit.target: Transformeringer brukes i en webdeler tilkobling til oversett data mellom to webdeler kontroller med inkompatible tilkoblingen punkt.

trans-unit.source: The RowToParametersTransformer class transforms data from a provider implementing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartRow> interface to a consumer expecting to receive data from a provider that implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartParameters> interface.
trans-unit.target: Klassen RowToParametersTransformer overfører data fra en leverandør implementering av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartRow>grensesnittet til en forbruker forventer å motta data fra en leverandør som implementerer den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartParameters>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartParameters> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartRow>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.RowToParametersTransformer"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.RowToParametersTransformer"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the list of names in the consumer that will receive the values from the provider.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir listen over navn i forbrukeren som skal motta verdiene fra leverandøren.

trans-unit.source: The ConsumerFieldNames property represents the fields in the consumer that will receive the transformed data from the provider.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ConsumerFieldNames representerer feltene i forbrukeren som skal motta transformerte data fra leverandøren.

trans-unit.source: The ConsumerFieldNames property can be set by the user through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.RowToParametersTransformer> configuration control, or set declaratively in the `<asp:RowToParametersTransformer />` element, where as many consumer field names as needed are assigned to the `ConsumerFieldNames` attribute, in the form `ConsumerFieldNames="fieldA,fieldB"`.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ConsumerFieldNames kan angis av brukeren fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.RowToParametersTransformer>konfigurasjonskontroll eller sett deklarativt i den `<asp:RowToParametersTransformer />` element, der så mange forbrukeren-feltnavn behov er tilordnet til den `ConsumerFieldNames` attributt i formatet `ConsumerFieldNames="fieldA,fieldB"`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.RowToParametersTransformer>

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.String> values representing the consumer fields.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref:System.String>verdiene som representerer de forbruker-feltene.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Provides an ASP.NET control that allows the user to configure a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.RowToParametersTransformer"></xref> transformer in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone"></xref> zone.
trans-unit.target: Gir en ASP.NET-kontroll som gir brukeren mulighet til å konfigurere en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.RowToParametersTransformer"> </xref> transformeringen i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone"> </xref> sone.

trans-unit.source: A Web Parts connection can be established statically or dynamically.
trans-unit.target: Kan opprette tilkobling webdeler statisk eller dynamisk.

trans-unit.source: A static connection is defined within the `<StaticConnections>` element.
trans-unit.target: En statisk tilkobling er definert i den `<StaticConnections>` elementet.

trans-unit.source: A user can define a dynamic connection when a connections zone is included in a Web page and the user is in the connect mode.
trans-unit.target: En bruker kan definere en dynamisk kobling når en Tilkoblingssone er inkludert i en webside og brukeren i connect-modus.

trans-unit.source: When establishing a dynamic connection, the user defines the connection through a configuration control.
trans-unit.target: Når du oppretter en dynamisk kobling definerer brukeren tilkoblingen via en konfigurasjonskontroll.

trans-unit.source: The CreateConfigurationControl method returns the control that the user interacts with to define the connection.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CreateConfigurationControl returnerer kontrollen som brukeren samhandler med til å definere tilkoblingen.

trans-unit.source: The configuration control displays a UI that allows the user to connect or disconnect a provider and consumer, and select which field from the provider row data to connect with the field data of the consumer.
trans-unit.target: Konfigurasjonskontrollen viser et grensesnitt som tillater brukeren å koble eller koble fra en leverandør og forbrukere, og Velg hvilket felt fra leverandøren raddata til å kommunisere med feltdata av en forbruker.

trans-unit.source: The control is displayed in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> zone.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen skal vises i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>

trans-unit.source: An ASP.NET control that displays a user interface (UI) that allows the user to configure a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.RowToParametersTransformer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En ASP.NET-kontroll som viser brukergrensesnittet (UI) som gir brukeren mulighet til å konfigurere en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.RowToParametersTransformer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The ProviderFieldNames property represents the fields in the provider that the transformer will pass to the consumer.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ProviderFieldNames representerer feltene i leverandøren transformeringen som skal sendes til brukeren.

trans-unit.source: The ProviderFieldNames property can be set by the user through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.RowToParametersTransformer> configuration control, or set declaratively in the `<asp:RowToParametersTransformer />` element, where as many provider field names as needed are assigned to the `ProviderFieldNames` attribute, in the form `ProviderFieldNames="fieldA,fieldB"`.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ProviderFieldNames kan angis av brukeren fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.RowToParametersTransformer>konfigurasjonskontroll eller sett deklarativt i den `<asp:RowToParametersTransformer />` element, der så mange feltet Leverandørnavn behov er tilordnet til den `ProviderFieldNames` attributt i formatet `ProviderFieldNames="fieldA,fieldB"`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.RowToParametersTransformer>

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.String> values representing the provider fields.
